The `AlignedLastCapturedFrames` implies that the depth images are not the original depth, but rather depth aligned to color. Therefore it is importation to verify that `&DepthIntrinsics` in the above code refers to the intrinsic of aligned depth.   
Also note that in the new aligned depth the location of the objects in the scene is different from original data and corresponds to the point-of-view of the color.

